<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.7.1">
<l>payiluñ cuṭaroḷi mūrttiyai paṅkayak kaṇṇaṉaip</l>
<l>payila viṉiyanam pāṟkaṭal cērnta paramaṉaip</l>
<l>payilun tiruvuṭai yāreva rēlu mavarkaṇṭīr</l>
<l>payilum piṟappiṭai tōṟemmai yāḷum paramarē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The form of dense glowing light, the lotus-eyed Kṛṣṇa,</l>
<l>our Highest one who joined the densely sweet milk ocean for our sake<note>This awkwardly placed nam is glossed by Periyavācaṉpiḷḷai as namakkāka, “for our sake”.</note></l>
<l>those who have the fortune to call [him], whoever they are, see,</l>
<l>are the highest ones who rule us in every reccurrent birth.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
